# KeryxPro - Phase 1 Implementation Plan

KeryxPro is a modern worship presentation software built for cross-platform desktop usage (Windows & macOS). This plan addresses the foundational Phase 1 goals: Window management, database setup, feature navigation, and control dashbaord setup.

